The,Ambari,API,is,a,user,friendly,Hadoop,management,portal,that,can,be,integrated,with,developers,own,applications,It,is,used,to,provide,manage,and,monitor,Apache,Hadoop,clusters,after,the,installation,of,the,clusters,When,using,the,Apache,Ambari,platform,provisioning,involves,the,installation,and,configuration,of,Hadoop,services,while,management,involves,the,manipulation,of,the,Hadoop,services,across,a,cluster,As,for,monitoring,system,administrators,can,use,the,platform,s,dashboard,to,track,the,performance,of,clusters,in,addition,to,gathering,metrics,and,setting,system,alerts